type: software
title: "Claude Ads"
abstract: >
  Multi-host paid advertising audit and optimization skill conforming to the
  Agent Skills open standard. Verified on Claude Code; experimental on OpenAI
  Codex CLI, Cursor, Windsurf, Gemini CLI, and Goose. Covers Google Ads
  (including AI Max), Meta Ads (including Andromeda + GEM + Lattice with
  Entity-ID clustering prediction), YouTube Ads, LinkedIn Ads, TikTok Ads,
  Microsoft Ads, Apple Ads, and Amazon Ads with 300+ audit checks, 22
  sub-skills, 11 parallel agents (including a regulatory-compliance agent
  covering the EU AI Act and the 22-state US privacy landscape), 12 industry
  templates, cross-platform attribution and server-side tracking deep dives,
  PPC math, A/B test design, PDF report generation, and a 41-test pytest eval
  harness.
